e:[["$","title","0",{"children":"Types of ISO 27001 Certification | WIZMS"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"The ISO/IEC 27001 certification demonstrates that the business adheres to the ISO 27001 standards and makes use of the best information security practices. "}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"ISO 27001 certification consultant in Dubai, ISO 27001 certification in Dubai, ISO 27001 certification in UAE"}],["$","meta","3",{"property":"og:title","content":"Types of ISO 27001 Certification | WIZMS"}],["$","meta","4",{"property":"og:description","content":"The ISO/IEC 27001 certification demonstrates that the business adheres to the ISO 27001 standards and makes use of the best information security practices. "}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://wizms.net/types-of-iso-27001-certification"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:type","content":"article"}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"article:published_time","content":"2026-01-02T06:32:02+00:00"}],["$","meta","8",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary"}],["$","meta","9",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"Types of ISO 27001 Certification | WIZMS"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"The ISO/IEC 27001 certification demonstrates that the business adheres to the ISO 27001 standards and makes use of the best information security practices. "}],["$","link","11",{"rel":"icon","href":"/favicon.ico"}],["$","$L27","12",{}]]
10:["$","p","11",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Environmental and Physical Security"}]
11:["$","p","12",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The organization's physical and environmental characteristics are covered in Annex A.11. It is the largest annexe, consisting of 15 domains split into two groups. Physical Security of ISO 27001 certification helps the organization to prevent unauthorized physical access, damage, or tampering with the organization's facilities is another objective of this domain1."}]
12:["$","p","13",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Administration Security"}]
13:["$","p","14",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"This Annex's main objective is to safeguard data processing facilities. It ensures that the business has sufficient safeguards in place to reduce the risk of infection and data loss. There are seven sections in Annex A.12."}]
14:["$","p","15",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Supply Chain Relationship"}]
15:["$","p","16",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"This appendix deals with contracts made between the organization and outside parties. It comes in two halves. Annex A.15.1 addresses the protection of a company's priceless assets that are reachable by or subject to the influence of suppliers. Annex A.15.2 ensures that all parties uphold the agreed-upon level of data security and service delivery."}]
16:["$","p","17",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Security Of Business Continuity Management System"}]
17:["$","p","18",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO 27001 consultants in UAE covers the protocols for documenting and handling security issues. It details which employee is responsible for a given assignment. This technique results in a uniform and effective approach to the incident and response lifecycle by identifying which employees should be held accountable for specific tasks."}]
18:["$","p","19",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Information Security Organization"}]
19:["$","p","20",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"It details which employee is responsible for a given assignment. This technique results in a uniform and effective approach to the incident and response lifecycle by identifying which employees should be held accountable for specific tasks."}]
1a:["$","p","21",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Asset Control"}]
1b:["$","p","22",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The identification of information assets by businesses and the attribution of protective duties are covered in this appendix. The main issue the ISO 27001 certification consultants in UAE and Dubai face is to identify the data assets that fall under ISMS"}]
1c:["$","p","23",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Cryptography"}]
1d:["$","p","24",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The security of private data and data encryption are the topics covered in this appendix. Its two controls ensure that businesses employ cryptography properly to protect data security, secrecy, and integrity."}]
1e:["$","p","25",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Administration Security"}]
1f:["$","p","26",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The main objective of administration security in ISO 27001 is to safeguard data processing facilities. It ensures that the business has sufficient safeguards in place to reduce the risk of infection and data loss."}]
20:["$","p","27",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"System acquisition, development, and upkeep of systems"}]
21:["$","p","28",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The information security is a top priority for all the oraganizations throughout the life cycle."}]
22:["$","p","29",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Management of information security"}]
23:["$","p","30",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"This covers the protocols for documenting and handling security issues. It details which employee is responsible for a given assignment."}]
24:["$","p","31",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO 27001 Compliance"}]
25:["$","p","32",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"This appendix helps the organization to identify relevant laws and rules so that it can better understand its obligations under the law and steer clear of any penalties."}]
26:["$","footer",null,{"className":"mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"flex flex-wrap gap-2","children":[["$","span","0",{"className":"text-xs font-semibold text-gray-600 bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded","children":"ISO 27001 certification consultant in Dubai"}],["$","span","1",{"className":"text-xs font-semibold text-gray-600 bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded","children":"ISO 27001 certification in Dubai"}],["$","span","2",{"className":"text-xs font-semibold text-gray-600 bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded","children":"ISO 27001 certification in UAE"}]]}]}]
